oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Lt. Col. J.Y. Kinsall sitting at his desk
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white photograph of Lt. Col. J.Y. Kinsall sitting at a desk. He is wearing an United States Air Force military uniform. On the desk there is a name plate, flowers, documents, etc.

Lt. Col. J.Y. Kinsall was the Director of Personnel and Administration Services at the Carswell Air Force Base located in Fort Worth, Texas. He was stationed at Carswell Air Force Base from 1943-1945.
